Project: ExRate (fintech CRM dashboard)

UI rules (must follow):
- Background: #EBECF0
- Cards: white, 12px radius, 1px light border, subtle shadow
- Spacing: 24px page padding; 16px inside cards; 12px gaps
- Typography: section titles semibold; key numbers bold; secondary text muted
- Reusable components: Sidebar, Topbar, Card, Tabs, TableRow
- No backend yet. Use mock data only.
- Keep consistent with the provided ExRate design.